question: do you ship joe&maisie together?
answer:
Hello anon :)

I’m a HUGE Gendrya fan, but i don’t particularly ship Maisie and Joe.

I mean… I absolutely LOVE their relationship/friendship, the respect they have for each other and the fact that they love/loved working together. But i don’t ship them romantically speaking.

I just want them to be happy (no matter with who) and to have a successful life and career.

But, of course, if one day they are together, god bless them. (Even if it’s not really our business…)

summary:
Daenerys going mad.
I love Daenerys, she's one of my favourite characters and I can only say I'm disappointed with how D&D have...
body:
Daenerys going mad.

I love Daenerys, she’s one of my favourite characters and I can only say I’m disappointed with how D&D have decided to show this. I’ve heard from other people that this is what George R R Martin wants to happen in the book, but tbf, she’s already hallucinating in the book, seeing and talking to people that aren’t there. Show!Dany should have had something like this, where she’s seen speaking to people that aren’t there, or something, this would have made more sense than her killing thousands of innocent people. I just don’t understand how she’s snapped so quickly. Maybe if wed gotten another season or more episodes, it could be believed,but it’s shitty writing and I’ll always have fan fiction to keep me going.
